# Invite required

`<%= @current_tenant.subdomain %>.<%= ENV['HOSTNAME'] %>` requires an invite code to join.

If you have an invite code, open this page with it to see the invite you are
being asked to accept:

    /invite-required?code=YOUR_CODE

Accepting an invite (which creates your membership) is an interactive
confirmation step — complete it in a browser.
